data.name: PageShape
desc: This service is for a page shape.

A page shape displays a preview of another page. These shapes are used inside notes pages to preview the corresponding drawing page. They're also used in the handout page to preview the printing position and order of pages

properties.name: PageNumber
desc: this is the page number that is used for the preview.
For page shapes on notes pages, this can't be changed. For page shapes on handout pages, this value only describes the relative order of the different page shapes on the page.
